도진，Yoon Do - jin）","name":"尹道振","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yoon Do Jin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"尹道振","primary":false}}]}},"person_1450858_translations":{"at":1773689209344,"data":{"id":1450858,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Imdb has wrong data again: nm7336746 is another instance of her","name":"Lam Thanh My","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"Lâm Thanh Mỹ là diễn viên nhí được khán giả biết đến rộng rãi qua vai Mận trong bộ phim Tôi Thấy Hoa Vàng Trên Cỏ Xanh. Khi đảm nhận vai diễn này, cô mới chỉ 10 tuổi, nhưng với khả năng diễn xuất tự nhiên và cảm xúc, Thanh Mỹ đã nhanh chóng chiếm được cảm tình của công chúng.\n\nDù còn nhỏ tuổi, cô đã góp mặt trong nhiều bộ phim khiến nhiều người bất ngờ về sự chăm chỉ và năng khiếu nghệ thuật của mình. Song song với việc đóng phim, Thanh Mỹ vẫn luôn chú trọng việc học, điều này càng khiến cô được khán giả yêu mến hơn.\n\nGần đây, nữ diễn viên nhí gây chú ý khi đăng tải những hình ảnh xinh đẹp ở tuổi 16, khiến cộng đồng mạng trầm trồ trước vẻ ngoài ngày càng trưởng thành.\n\nSinh ra trong một gia đình không có truyền thống nghệ thuật, Lâm Thanh Mỹ đến với diễn xuất khá tình cờ — cô bắt đầu đóng quảng cáo sau khi được mẹ dắt đi casting và may mắn được chọn, mở ra con đường nghệ thuật từ rất sớm.","name":"Lam Thanh My","primary":true}}]}},"person_225411_translations":{"at":1773689210322,"data":{"id":225411,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Mark O'Brien (born May 7th, 1984) is a Canadian actor and director. He is best known for playing the role of Des Courtney in Republic of Doyle (2010) and Tom Rendon in Halt and Catch Fire (2014).","name":"Mark O'Brien","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Mark O’Brien (* 7. Mai 1984 in St. John’s, Neufundland und Labrador) ist ein kanadischer Schauspieler.\n\nDer aus St. John’s stammende Mark O’Brien begann seine Schauspielkarriere in lokalen Theatern. Seine erste größere Rolle hatte er als Drake 2006 in der Miniserie Above and Beyond. Im selben Jahr war er für zehn Folgen in der Serie You’re It! zu sehen. 2009 hatte er eine Rolle im Film Grown Up Movie Star neben Shawn Doyle und Tatiana Maslany inne. Seit 2010 gehört er als Des Courtney zur Hauptbesetzung der Serie Republic of Doyle – Einsatz für zwei. Im Jahr 2011 folgte ein Auftritt in der Serie Warehouse 13 sowie im Jahr 2012 einer in Murdoch Mysteries.\n\nQuelle: Wikipedia","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Марк О'Брайен","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"马克·奥布莱恩（Mark O'Brien，1984年5月7日-），加拿大演员、导演。他最出名的是在《道尔共和国》（2010 年）中扮演德斯·考特尼 （Des Courtney） 和在《停火》（2014 年）中扮演汤姆·伦登 （Tom Rendon）。","name":"马克·奥布莱恩","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"馬克·奧布萊恩（Mark O'Brien，1984 年 5 月 7 日-），加拿大演員、導演。他最出名的是在《道爾共和國》（2010 年）中扮演德斯·考特尼 （Des Courtney） 和在《停火》（2014 年）中扮演湯姆·倫登 （Tom Rendon）。","name":"馬克·奧布萊恩","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Марк О’Браєн","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"マーク・オブライエン","primary":false}}]}},"tv_285636_keywords":{"at":1773689213668,"data":{"id":285636,"results":[{"name":"miniseries","id":11162}]}},"person_2100103_translations":{"at":1773689215191,"data":{"id":2100103,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Michael Vitovich","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_1225474_translations":{"at":1773689217105,"data":{"id":1225474,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"Η Jacqueline Lourdes Blanco Davao είναι Φιλιππινέζα ηθοποιός και εκπαιδευτής αεροβικής, ισπανικής καταγωγής. Κατά τη διάρκεια της δεκαετίας του 1980 και της δεκαετίας του 1990, εμφανίστηκε σε διαφορετικά κινηματογραφικά είδη, συμπεριλαμβανομένων των Hihintayin Kita sa Langit Si Aida, Si Lorna, o Si Fe Misis mo, Misis ko και Palabra de honor.\n\nΗ Blanco είναι κόρη του διάσημου συνθέτη και ηθοποιού της Μουσικής των Φιλιππίνων Pilita Corrales. Έχει έναν ετεροθαλή αδερφό που ονομάζεται Ramon Christopher Gutierrez. Είναι παντρεμένη με τον φιλιππινέζο ηθοποιό Ricky Davao. Έχουν τρία παιδιά.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jacqueline Lourdes Corrales Blanco-Davao (born February 11, 1964) is a Filipino actress and aerobic instructor. During the 1980s and the 1990s, she appeared in different film genres including Hihintayin Kita sa Langit, (1991), Si Aida, Si Lorna, o Si Fe, (1989) Misis Mo, Misis Ko, (1988) and Palabra de Honor (1983).\n\nBlanco co-hosted the noontime show Student Canteen on GMA Network from 1982 until the show's cancellation in 1986. She was also a regular fixture on the Sunday musical extravaganza GMA Supershow on the same network. In 1999, she became a household name when she played the main antagonist in the ABS-CBN primetime drama series Saan Ka Man Naroroon. Her television appearances include a regular co-hosting stint in Walang Tulugan from 2008 to 2016, and the sitcom Vampire ang Daddy Ko, where she and her mother Pilita Corrales alternated for the role of Sonya Ventura as the older/younger versions.\n\nIn June 2007, she enrolled in the Associate of Arts program of the University of the Philippines, Open University. Blanco wrote a column in The Philippine Star newspaper.\n\nSince the 2000s, she has remained frequent with GMA-7 in afternoon and primetime dramas.","name":"Jackie Lou Blanco","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PH","iso_639_1":"tl","name":"","english_name":"Tagalog","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jackie Lou Blanco","primary":true}}]}},"person_193020_translations":{"at":1773689217160,"data":{"id":193020,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Richard Glover is an actor, known for Into the Woods (2014), A Field in England (2013) and Sightseers (2012).","name":"Richard Glover","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"理查德·格洛弗是一位演员，以《走进森林》（2014 年）、《英格兰的田野》（2013 年）和《观光者》（2012 年）而闻名。","name":"理查德·格洛弗","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"理查德·格洛弗是一位演員，以《走進森林》（2014 年）、《英格蘭的田野》（2013 年）和《觀光者》（2012 年）而聞名。","name":"理查德·格洛弗","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ричард Гловер","primary":false}}]}},"person_3247887_translations":{"at":1773689217399,"data":{"id":3247887,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"임기홍","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Im Gi-hong","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"林基弘","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"F